data.eml:eml: Revision of the Alpheus websteri Kingsley, 1880 species complex (Crustacea: Decapoda: Alpheidae), with revalidation of A. arenensis (Chace, 1937)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Anker, Arthur, Hurt, Carla, Knowlton, Nancy (2008): Revision of the Alpheus websteri Kingsley, 1880 species complex (Crustacea: Decapoda: Alpheidae), with revalidation of A. arenensis (Chace, 1937). Zootaxa 1694: 51-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.180675
